        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 15 at 7:07AM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>Moderate to heavy snow showers as pass level this morning will
reduce visibilities to below a mile at times. Warming pavement
temperatures will keep slushy snow accumulations minor, generally
less than an inch. Travelers should be prepared for variable
driving conditions.
